      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RED ROCK RATTLER (2) was strong over this course and distance last time despite filling the minors, finishing 4.5 lengths behind Coco Mac in 18.60 and recording a new PB here. Going well and rates on top. SWIFT ELI (5) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (25.55) at Gunnedah behind Ava's Milo in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Must be included in calculations. ROSACKY RAYO (1) turned in a plain effort last time when eighth at Richmond over 401m behind Zipping Marquez (23.67) in a Grade 4/5. Has ability and is one of the better chances. HYBRID BLUE (3) is a last-start placegetter at this track and distance - in the mix again.",
